  "slug": "two-players-one-horse",
  "title": "Two Players One Horse",
  "description": "This mod allows two players to mount together on the same horse. Epic!",
  "body": "---\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2f1dce66b2bdadeb026c61a8b10f80bf24110442.webp\" alt=\"About the mod\" width=\"850\">\n</p>\n\n\n<p align='right'><font face=\"Minecraft, Minecraftia, Courier\"><font color=\"\"><font size=\"4\"><em>Have you ever wished to be able to ride a horse...<br>while your friend sits behind you to back you up in battle?</em></font></font></font></p>\n\n<p align='right'><font face=\"Minecraft, Minecraftia, Courier\"><font color=\"\"><font size=\"6\"><strong>Well, now you can!!</strong></font></font></font></p>\n\n---\n<p align='right'><font face=\"Minecraft, Minecraftia, Courier\"><font color=\"\"><font size=\"4\"><em>This mod allows two players to mount on the same horse...<br></em><strong><font size=\"5\">together!</font></strong></font></font></font></p>\n\n---\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5397ce5921360f3d628164235db1e34864ed4494.webp\" alt=\"Features of the mod\" width=\"850\">\n</p>\n\n\n- <font face=\"Minecraft, Minecraftia, Courier\"><font color=\"\"><font size=\"5\">🐎<font size=\"4\"> Right click on the horse to join the ride!</font></font></font></font>\n- <font face=\"Minecraft, Minecraftia, Courier\"><font color=\"\"><font size=\"5\">🔄<font size=\"4\"> Control of the horse can be switched at any time</font></font></font></font>\n- <font face=\"Minecraft, Minecraftia, Courier\"><font color=\"\"><font size=\"5\">🏇<font size=\"4\"> Only the player sitting in front has control over the horse movement</font></font></font></font>\n- <font face=\"Minecraft, Minecraftia, Courier\"><font color=\"\"><font size=\"5\">🏹<font size=\"4\"> The player sitting behind can freely turn around and open their inventory. This may prove very handy in battles!</font></font></font></font>\n- <font face=\"Minecraft, Minecraftia, Courier\"><font color=\"\"><font size=\"5\">🐴<font size=\"4\"> The mod also works for Donkeys and Mules</font></font></font></font>\n---\n<p><br></p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/beethoven92\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/432444/description_9a6503c8-b60b-45f5-ab92-af69fb418d2f.png\" alt=\"Ko-Fi banner\" width=\"247\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n---",
